Class ServerNamespace

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.sonar.Namespace
us.mn.state.dot.sonar.server.ServerNamespace
public class ServerNamespace extends Namespace
A SONAR namespace is a mapping from all SONAR names to types, objects and attributes.

Douglas Lau
